doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible', content='IE=edge')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
    link(href='/_/bootstrap.min.css', rel='stylesheet')
    link(href='/_/sticky-footer.css', rel='stylesheet')
  title= title
  body
    script(src='https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.0.slim.min.js',integrity='sha256-AMg3I7ya76OLPD9M+Mk7kqrA29HUn/FuGBfT/9Uf9ls=',crossorigin='anonymous')
    main(role='main',class='container')
      center
        a(href='/')
          img(src='/_/ir1.png',style='max-width:90%')
      hr
      .row
        .col
          center
            h3= repo
      br
      p
        | Here are the 10 oldest issues (by update date).  Can you help push them forward?
      table
        each item in data
          tr
            td(style='padding:5px')
              a(href=item.html_url,target='_blank')
                img(src=item.user.avatar_url,width='30')
            td(style='padding:5px')
              a(href=item.html_url,target='_blank')
                b= item.title
      hr
      .row
        .col
          p
            | Keeping a project healthy is tough, and many projects
            | get overwhelmed and need all the help they can get.  Want to make a difference?
            | Pick a repository and see if you can help with the oldest issues!

      .row
        .col
          center
            input#repo.form-control(placeholder='facebook/rocksdb',autocomplete='off',autocorrect='off',autocapitalize='off',spellcheck='false')
            br
            input#gorepo.btn.btn-primary(value='Go')
            script.
              $('#repo').on('keyup', function(e) {
                if (e.keyCode == 13) {
                  $('#gorepo').trigger('click')
                }
              })
              $('#gorepo').click(function() {
                var x = $('#repo').val()
                if (x.indexOf('/') !== -1 && x.length > x.indexOf('/')) {
                  window.location = '/' + x
                }
              })
      hr
      .row
        .col
          p
            | Easily access or link to any repo by appending the organization and repo to our URL.
            | i.e. <a href="https://issue.rodeo/facebook/rocksdb">https://issue.rodeo/facebook/rocksdb</a>
    footer.footer
      .container
        span.text-muted
          | Created by Fosco Marotto
